tural and stacking properties (Fig. 2e).Fig. 2Intrinsic photostabilities of A–D–A NFAs.
a Molecular structures of FREA IT-4F, SFRA HF-PCIC, and NFRA PTIC. b–d Their film UV–vis absorption spectra and photo images (before and after 64 h) under one-sun-equivalent illumination in ambient. e The change and f, the percentage of remaining absorption intensity at 64 h illumination. g Energy levels for different acceptors. EH 2-ethylhexyl.
